name: W3css.Button

values.name: btn
values.comment:
Creates w3Css button.
A rectangular button with a shadow hover effect.
Default color is black.

    button [][ text "Button" ]
values.type: List (W3css.Types.Option msg) -> List (Html.Html msg) -> Html.Html msg

values.name: button
values.comment:
Creates w3Css button.
A rectangular button with a gray hover effect.
Default color is light-gray in W3.CSS version 3.
Default color is inherited from parent element in version 4.

    button [][ text "Button" ]
values.type: List (W3css.Types.Option msg) -> List (Html.Html msg) -> Html.Html msg

name: W3css.Margins

values.name: margin
values.comment: Adds a 16px margin to all sides of an element

values.name: marginBottom
values.comment: Adds a 16px bottom margin to an element

values.name: marginLeft

values.name: marginRight
values.comment: Adds a 16px right margin to an element

values.name: marginTop
values.comment: Adds a 16px top margin to an element

values.name: section
values.comment: Adds a 16px top and bottom margin to an element
